summary: I want to spread some love!!  If you are a visual artist submit to me 2-4 of your favourite pictures, your name, maybe a little...
body:
I want to spread some love!!

If you are a visual artist submit to me 2-4 of your favourite pictures, your name, maybe a little bit bout your art and add your art blog or portfolio. I will reblog them later that day and hope I can spread some love!

Be it original art or fanart of any fandom! I won’t post nsfw or graphic violence.

If you don’t want to submit but rather make your own post this is fine too. You can tag me or as Tumblr might eat up tags just dm me the link to your post and I reblog it.

Offer is open until 4 pm EST.

#spreadthelove #artist2018

blog.name: autonomy1
blog.title: Peter Percival-AUTONOMY
blog.description: Shades, nuances, scraps of existence......looking directly at an object can sometimes be a meaningless, even a destructive use of time…in society we are trained to look at things quickly, process that information and move on to another view…so much information and meaning can be lost in the action of moving on….by changing the expected angle of view, or re-arranging elements of an image one can derive another meaning from it, and if not an absolute meaning an abstract one which makes us look once again…that is all one can ask for, another look…(©) Pete Percival - 2013 All Rights Reserved. Reproduction of any kind is illegal.
